releaseUsage

public static void releaseUsage(String feature,
                                String user,
                                com.conceptwave.scripting.Object capacity)
Release feature usage. NOTE: The features is not released automatically when user session ends on timeout. Provide an event handler for SYSTEM_SESSION_LOGOUT event and release all features by releaseUsageByUser() method.

Parameters:
feature - Feature name
user - Optional: user ID
capacity - Usage value. If not specified, the value is 1.

requestUsage

public static void requestUsage(String feature,
                                String user,
                                com.conceptwave.scripting.Object capacity)
Request feature usage. The capacity will be hold until it's released. NOTE: The features is not released automatically when user session ends on timeout. Provide an event handler for SYSTEM_SESSION_LOGOUT event and release all features by releaseUsageByUser() method.

Parameters:
feature - Feature name
user - Optional: user ID
capacity - Usage value. If not specified, the value is 1.
